        "subject": "LU-1821 osc: fix build error with newer gcc",
        "message": "LU-1821 osc: fix build error with newer gcc\n\nosc_setup is forgetting error when ptlrpcd_alloc_work fails.\nAnd it causes build error.\n\ncc1: warnings being treated as errors\nosc_request.c:3581: error: ignoring return value of ‘PTR_ERR’,\ndeclared with attribute warn_unused_result\n\nSigned-off-by: Peng Tao <tao.peng@emc.com>\nChange-Id: Ib36fefa9d33a49cfa7dbacd8e47190f467aa7d23\n"
